@concat('SELECT [FlightPlanId]
,[DataType]
,[AlternateRouteAirportIATACode]
,[WaypointSequenceId]
,b.value as [Function]
,[TCreatedId]
,[TLoadDate]
,[TFileName]

 cross APPLY openjson(
    case when Left([Function],1) =''['' 
     then [Function] 
     else ''["''+[Function]+''"]'' end ,''$'') b
where tfilename = ''',pipeline().parameters.InputFileName,''';')
